                "invention-title": [
                    "Method and device for directly smelting zinc through hydrogen-based gas phase reduction and application of method and device",
                    "氢基气相还原直接炼锌的方法、装置及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for directly smelting zinc by hydrogen-based gas-phase reduction of a hydrogen-based gas-phase reducing agent, which comprises the following steps: adding a lead-zinc oxide material and a gas-phase reducing agent into a molten pool reduction furnace, and melting the mixed material to obtain a lead-zinc-copper melt; a hydrogen-based gas-phase reducing agent is introduced into the molten pool reduction furnace, and the hydrogen-based gas-phase reducing agent and the lead-zinc-copper melt are subjected to a reduction reaction; the adding amount of the hydrogen-based gas-phase reducing agent is 0.8-1.5 times of the amount of the gas-phase reducing agent required for completely converting gas-phase CO2 in the reduction furnace of the molten pool into CO; carrying out reduction reaction on the lead-zinc-copper melt to obtain crude lead alloy, zinc steam and slag; the zinc vapor reacts with a gas-phase reducing agent and then enters a flue to be recycled to obtain metal zinc, and a porous carbon material is lined on the lower portion of the flue. The method can directly recover the metal zinc in a simple substance form, and meets the requirements of short-process low-carbon development in the metallurgical industry."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种利用氢基气相还原剂氢基气相还原直接炼锌的方法，包括步骤：向熔池还原炉中加入铅锌氧化物料以及气相还原剂，所述混合物料熔融后，得铅锌铜熔体；向所述熔池还原炉中通入氢基气相还原剂，所述氢基气相还原剂与所述铅锌铜熔体进行还原反应；所述氢基气相还原剂的加入量为将所述熔池还原炉内气相CO2全部转化为CO所需气相还原剂量的0.8～1.5倍；所述铅锌铜熔体经还原反应得粗铅合金、锌蒸气以及炉渣；所述锌蒸气与气相还原剂反应后进入烟道回收得金属锌，其中，所述烟道下部内衬有多孔碳材。本发明能够以单质形态直接回收金属锌，符合冶金行业短流程低碳发展的要求。"
                }
            ]
